{"id": "1454663168176558113", "channel_id": "1454662875766460528", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "使用雷婭試訓時，發現每次算力上限扣除後都會重計當前算力，且重置無法清除該效果", "timestamp": "2025-12-28T02:32:05.628000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-28T02:34:53.587000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1454662875766460528", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「处理中」相位算力上限", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1454664182245883946", "channel_id": "1454662875766460528", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "ex：試訓初始10算力上限\n使用鼠鼠的智慧，-1到雷婭身上\n每回結束不滿10自動+1，下回會變10\n\n使用鼠鼠的智慧，-1到雷婭身上\n使用雷婭 歡愉果實+1上限，再用鼠鼠的智慧(第二個)\n每回結束不滿10自動+1，下回理論上該變10，但僅有9，因為第二次使用時直接以初始10(當前最大或其他?)減去兩層的算力上限減少效果", "timestamp": "2025-12-28T02:36:07.401000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-28T03:40:44.414000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1454662875766460528", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「处理中」相位算力上限", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
